messages.text: Why would Derek try to kill Sasha?
Did he know she had doubts about living at the house?
Or that she was upset about him breaking up with her?
I don't know, Andrea.
All I've got is Celia's diary.
But it seems to me like he tried to kill her.
If he just wanted her to get amnesia, pushing her onto the rocks would be too risky.
Yeah. He must have wanted her dead.
Or wait.
Maybe she did fall, and when she got amnesia, it all worked out OK for him.
Like, he went along with it.
If she fell, he should have taken her straight to the hospital.
But he didn't.
He lied to her about her identity.
He didn't even call her parents to tell them she's OK.
He let them think she had died.
He went to her fucking funeral, Em!
And he lied to the police about what happened at the beach.
Whoa. Yeah. You're right.
No matter how you look at it, he's guilty of something.
Could you tell Sasha about the beach?
Like jog her memory or whatever?
I don't know if that works like in the movies.
Why didn't Celia do anything about it?
If she knew what happened to Sasha, why did she stay in the house?
Why did she keep going through tests to join The Order?
I think I know the answer to that, actually.
It's in her diary.
Celia wrote that the three tests are called The Trials.
She had just finished The Breaking and was on her vow of silence when Derek took Sasha to the beach.
But Sasha died seven months ago.
If Celia was on her vow of silence when Sasha went to the beach, why did she just now do The Cleansing tonight?
Apparently Derek made her do an extended vow of silence.
Why?
I don't know.
But Celia wrote in her diary she was getting scared of Derek because of what happened to Sasha.
Then why did she stay at the house?
She was even more afraid to leave The Order.
What? Why?
She wrote about where she came from.
She was a teenage runaway from an abusive home.
Oh shit.
She had no money, no family or friends outside The Order.
She had nowhere else to go.
And it seems like Derek brainwashed her enough to believe in the End Times.
After what she wrote about living on the streets, I can see why she fell prey to his bullshit charm.
Her diary isn't an easy read.
Whoa. That's terrible.
I feel bad for looking at it, but I needed more information.
Poor Celia. She was 15.
She died too young.
OMG.
Derek is a psychopath.
We gotta get Kate out.
And you!
I feel like we're in way over our heads here.
Me too. But we'll think of something.
Isn't the diary enough evidence for the cops?
I don't know if they can prove what Celia wrote is the truth.
Well, Sasha being alive proves something, right?
Why can't we call for help, Em?!
Because as soon as Derek hears those sirens out there, he'll know it was me and I'm a goner.
Please. Give me some time to think.
I gotta go.
They're about to do bed checks.
Bed checks?!
I think some of them are freaked out about Celia.
It's getting stricter around here already.
My battery's at 23% now.
I still haven't found where Derek hid my charger.
We're running out of time.
Talk soon.
The next morning.
Emily?
Please. I'm sick with worrying.
What's going on in the house?
I've kept my phone on all night in case you texted.
My battery's at 41%.
PLEASE.
I'm here. I've got bad news.
OMG. Is it Kate?!
No. Kate's OK.
But Derek made a big announcement after breakfast.
Are you still at the old stone mill?
Yeah. I've been waiting to hear from you before I went out looking.
What did Derek announce?
The End Times.
Excuse me?
He said "the End Times are nigh."
Sasha told him she had a dream last night about a big fire.
A fire?
Yeah. Like the house going up in flames.
Smoke everywhere.
Burnt flesh. Ew.
He said she's The Herald and she's telling them news of the End Times.
Wait. No. She's not talking about the End Times.
Yeah, no shit.
No, I mean the fire really happened to her.
Huh?
Her house burned down when she was 8.
Her brother got burnt some. He recovered OK but his skin is scarred.
She went unconscious from the smoke and a fireman carried her out of the house.
She had nightmares about it for a long time.
OMG. She remembers something from before the beach?
Well, her subconscious does, I guess.
But she thinks it's a dream, right?
Yeah, but maybe we can get her to remember more.
Wait. What's the bad news?
Derek thinking it's the apocalypse isn't exactly a shocker.
Because the End Times are here, he said the recruits need to be inducted into The Order ASAP.
The Trials are on a new schedule now.
Kate's Confession is tonight at 5.
And I go into the cell for The Breaking tomorrow morning.
I need help, Andrea.
OK. I'm going to find the house.
I'm getting you and Kate out of there somehow.
OK. Phone's going off to save battery.
I'm at 11%.
Keep yours on, OK?
I will.
Hurry. PLEASE.
5 hours and 50 minutes later.
ANDREA.
Answer me!
What? I'm here!
I'm still hopelessly lost in the woods.
Thank God I brought some food and water.
LISTEN.
Kate confessed on me.
WHAT?!
I thought her note said she wouldn't tell?
I guess the coming apocalypse scared her enough to think twice about it.
She told the entire Order about the questions I asked her.
They got really suspicious.
I need your help!
I'm in the woods now, too.
Call me, Em!
I can't.
I'm hiding nearby the house.
They're out looking for me.
They might hear me if I'm talking on the phone.
What the hell happened?!
Kate talked about her sins and guilt and it all seemed OK.
Normal stuff about cheating on a test or borrowing your clothes without asking.
But at the end of The Confession, she told them about our notes.
She said I'm a secret spy of the Devil!
Derek looked freaking pissed.
I ran out of the house and climbed the fence into the woods.
But why are you still hiding by the house?
Run, Emily!
Get to the old stone mill. I'll meet you there.
I can't.
I got hurt.
OMG. Are you OK?! What's wrong?
I think I broke my ankle after I fell over the fence.
I can barely hobble around.
They're gonna find me out here!
Derek will kill me!
I'm still looking for you but we gotta call the police now.
You need medical help.
But we don't know where the house is.
How will we give the cops an address?
The GPS doesn't seem to help much out here.
I think they can track our phones.
They have technology we don't.
Please, Em.
Fine. But you have to do it.
I gotta stay quiet.
OK. I'm calling 911, Em.
Hold on for me.
Battery's at 5%.
HURRY.
6 minutes later.
The police are tracking my phone, Em.
I've got 20% battery.
I hope they're quick about it.
Are you OK?
I have 3% battery.
My phone's gonna die, Andrea!
Stay where you are.
I'm looking all around for you.
OMG.
Sasha found me.
WHAT?!
Emily?
Em?!
Hello?
4 minutes later.
Hello, Andrea.
Are you trying to text your friend Emily?
Sasha?! Is that you?
My name is Regina.
But your friend is calling me Sasha.
You keep on texting her.
I got your name and number from her phone.
Good thing I did because her battery's nearly dead.
Derek took the charger.
What do you want?!
I want you to forget about Emily.
OMG. No.
Please don't hurt her!
Oh, I won't.
But Derek will.
I'm gonna call him and tell him where she is out here.
I swear she won't tell anyone about The Order.
Why can't you just let her go?
And let my sister go, too. PLEASE.
Kate.
Emily just told me Kate's your sister.
I've had to lie to my mom and tell her Kate's out of town with some new friends.
She's been worried sick about her.
Please.
Kate is scheduled for The Cleansing tomorrow afternoon.
And she could've left if she wanted to.
She likes it here.
Derek brainwashed her.
Like he brainwashed you.
You don't know anything about me.
I know a lot about you, Sasha.
I'm Regina.
You were my best friend in high school.
I didn't go to high school, Andrea.
I studied here at The Order with Derek.
No. You met Derek when we went to college.
He took over your life, Sasha.
You stopped talking to me.
To all of our friends.
You were always off with Derek and his creepy cult.
Stop telling lies.
The Order isn't a cult.
I knew even then it was something bad.
I tried to help you but you didn't seem to hear me.
You just spouted off the nonsense Derek filled your head with.
And then you DIED, Sasha.
What the hell are you talking about?
You went to the beach with Derek and he said you drowned.
The Coast Guard couldn't find your body.
They looked for weeks before you were declared dead.
I went to your funeral. Your mom and dad are still devastated.
No. They died when I was 8. I'm an orphan.
They're alive, Sasha.
REGINA.
But I know what really happened when you were 8.
What?
Your house burned down.
That's why you dreamed about it.
It's not a sign of the End Times.
It fucking happened to you, Sasha.
Derek pushed you onto the rocks at the beach. You got amnesia.
He gave you the name Regina.
He lied to you.
YOU are lying to me.
Derek said the demons of the Devil tell lies.
I won't be fooled by you.
The End Times are nigh.
Please.
Let Kate and Emily go.
Absolutely not.
Hear me out.
You have a birthmark on your inner thigh.
Excuse me?!
You used to laugh about it because you thought it looked like a dragonfly.
That's why you got that tattoo on your wrist.
You said it connected you to the dragon world.
You joked that you could breathe fire.
I never said anything of the sort.
You have the birthmark, don't you?
Sasha?
Look, I don't know how you found out about my birthmark.
Maybe your friend Emily peeked at me in the shower or something.
But I don't believe you about any of this shit.
I've never been to the beach.
I called the cops, Sasha. They tracked my phone.
They'll be there soon.
Seriously?!
You called THE POLICE?!
They'll kill us all, Andrea!
Derek said they are agents of the Devil.
If you let Emily go, I won't tell the cops anything about you.
You can escape before they get to the house.
Fuck. Fine.
I won't tell Derek where Emily is but you've gotta rescue her and Kate yourself.
I'm getting the hell outta here.
Thank you, Sasha!
Sasha?
Regina?
2 minutes later.
Andrea, I've got 1% battery.
So shut the fuck up and listen to me before it runs out.
Sasha ran off and left me in the woods.
She didn't call Derek.
I know. The cops will be there soon.
ANDREA.
Derek called me.
He's got Kate in the cell.
WHAT?!
I don't think he knows you called 911.
Or that I'm too hurt to move.
He said I've got 1 hour to get back to the house.
OMG. Or what?!
Or he will poison Kate.
